sentences: Twennynine, also known as Twennynine with Lenny White, was an American R&B band founded in 1979.
Twennynine was founded by jazz fusion drummer Lenny White in 1979 after he left Return to Forever.
They released their debut album Best of Friends on Elektra Records in 1979.
Their sophomore album Twennynine with Lenny White was released in 1980, with White and Dunn again as producers.
Twennynine performed on American Bandstand and The Mike Douglas Show in 1980.
Twennynine released their third album Just Like Dreamin' in 1981.
The group split up in 1983, after which Lenny White returned to jazz session work.
